The paper discusses a tool for detecting plagiarism in answer-set programming, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The tool also has applications in software engineering (cs.SE) and machine learning (cs.LG) as it uses algorithms for pattern matching and similarity detection. Additionally, the paper discusses the security aspect of plagiarism detection, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
